::Striker::

Striker sets off after Spears, his eyes wide from her kiss.

"Um... That's ok..." he mumbles, a sudden pain in his side.

"Argh!" he grunts, falling to his knees, his hand shimmering. He looks at 
Spears, getting to his feet.

"The space-time continuim is breaking up a bit," he says to her, his hand 
continuing to shimmer (in other words: my owner is going on vacation so I'll 
be gone till he gets back), "I'll phaze out for a few days, I'll be back in a 
bit!"

With that, the shimmering covers his whole body, Striker dissapearing with a 
bright flash.
